name: Chromatose Eye Shadow: 9 PC. Full Set
description:
“CHROMATOSE” .... a nine color line of cleverly culled chromatone eye shadow colors. With handy reusable packaging and animal-friendly attitude, these loud and beautiful colors are undeniably cool in the truest sense of the word.

	Full Set includes: Panther Power, Electric Envy, Sailor’s Song, Blitz Blonde, Mod Metal, Loud Lilac, Pretty Penny, Flamingo Fever, and Dark Denim.  Comes in reusable cosmetics pouch.
